{"tid":1651552,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"薯仔炮制造方法","createTime":"2019-10-13T11:24:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T11:24:20.000Z","uid":297623,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bf8e5075c7c88ff1c9dca9f2d4b0f63e1572b851","tid":1651552,"uid":297623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T11:24:20.000Z","msg":"材料:<br />\n<br />\n四吋尾蓋(圖二左)<br />\n四吋轉二吋接駁(圖2右)<br />\n四吋白pvc膠喉 一呎<br />\n兩吋白pvc膠喉 一呎半<br />\n四吋梳件 兩件<br />\n打火制(最好用呢個，揾唔到既買個電子火機，睇圖1)/火槍<br />\nPVC膠水/還氧樹脂膠<br />\n釘膠/填縫膠<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G6Vh3QN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG6Vh3QN.jpg&h=35fdef5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n注意事項<br />\n1.接駁位用pvc膠水或者環氧樹脂加黐在一起<br />\n2.用 釘膠或填縫膠把縫封上<br />\n3.不要加太多發射藥，小心tk<br />\n<br />\n圖1<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cPj3eLn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcPj3eLn.jpg&h=156c0d81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖2<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SOL6cBY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSOL6cBY.png&h=9cdf112f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n完成後大約一米<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FweyB5S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFweyB5S.jpg&h=3b9ca308&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用法<br />\n1. 發彈藥放進一( 隨你喜歡用什麼都可以 反正大小大概為四吋左右 不要太大不要太細 ,最好用報紙 皮球 薯仔)<br />\n2.把3打開<br />\n3. 把發射藥放進2(用易燃氣體,可以用除塵罐)<br />\n呢一種<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zih01BE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzih01BE.jpg&h=f49c5254&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.把3快速蓋上<br />\n5. 瞄準目標<br />\n6.fire!!!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aygtq3F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAygtq3F.jpg&h=479da91e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有錯勿屌"}]}